  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Logistics Operations Specialist",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Descriptions:</strong></p><ol><li><p><strong>Inbound coordination:</strong> arrange deliveries from suppliers, book receiving slots, check PO/DO, handle discrepancies/damages, and follow up on backorders.</p></li><li><p><strong>Outbound fulfillment:</strong> process sales orders, create pick/pack lists, schedule courier/lorry, prepare delivery documents, and ensure OTIF (on-time, in-full).</p></li><li><p><strong>Inventory control:</strong> monitor stock levels, reconcile system vs physical stock, manage cycle counts/stocktakes, investigate variances, and reduce shrinkage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Warehouse operations:</strong> coordinate picking/packing standards, carton labeling, palletizing, storage location control, and improve layout/workflow.</p></li><li><p><strong>Transport & 3PL coordination:</strong> liaise with forwarders, couriers, and 3PL warehouses on lead times, claims, service levels, and rate comparisons.</p></li><li><p><strong>Shipping & export/import documents (if applicable):</strong> prepare/verify commercial invoice, packing list, BL/AWB, COO, HS codes, and coordinate customs clearance.</p></li><li><p><strong>Returns & reverse logistics:</strong> manage customer returns, exchange/credit processes, RTV to suppliers, and quarantine/expiry handling.</p></li><li><p><strong>Systems & reporting:</strong> update ERP/WMS, track KPIs (delivery performance, accuracy, inventory days), and produce daily/weekly operations reports.</p></li><li><p><strong>Cost & process improvement:</strong> optimize delivery routes/packaging, reduce logistics cost, improve SOPs, and troubleshoot operational bottlenecks.</p></li><li><p><strong>Compliance & safety:</strong> follow SOPs for workplace safety, storage requirements, and (where relevant) regulated items handling.</p></li></ol><p>Requirements :</p><ul><li>Min 1 year of experience in distribution or supply chain industry.</li><li>Have forklift licence.</li><li>Physically fit and healthy</li></ul>",
